Thursday, October. 10 2019

South Florida Condo & HOA Expo

   Get legal insights, financial advice, communication tips, proactive
   management solutions and much more from the region's top professionals.
   Attend FREE educational seminars and CEU courses covering all of
   today's essential property management topics.

Thursday, October. 10 2019

CMB Community Health and Wellness Fair

   Join us on Thursday, October 10 for a free community health and
   wellness fair! Guests will enjoy: – Free Massages – Medical Screenings
   – Flu Shots – Food Demos – Raffles & more!

